\subsection{\textsc{prayer for mission}}

Almighty and everlasting God, who alone workest great marvels: Send down upon our clergy and the congregations committed to their charge the life-giving Spirit of thy grace, shower them with the continual dew of thy blessing, and ignite in them a zealous love of thy Gospel; through Jesus Christ our Lord. \textbf{Amen.}

